ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of RODNEY NELSON of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of History, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective March 12, 2018, in the place of Ken Langille, whose term has expired.
